Class Parent

java.lang.Object
Player
Parent
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, PlayGame
public class Parent extends Player implements Serializable
Parent class representing a player with parental controls. This class extends Player and encapsulates the additional functionality for managing parental restrictions such as authentication, playtime tracking, setting play limits, and pet revival. It implements the Serializable interface for parent account creation purposes.
